# 6. Core Templates

---

# Template 1: Opposite Direction

```java
int left = 0;
int right = arr.length - 1;

while(left < right){

    if(condition){
        return answer;
    }
    else if(arr[left] + arr[right] < target){
        left++;
    }
    else{
        right--;
    }
}
```

---

# Template 2: Same Direction

```java
int slow = 0;

for(int fast = 0; fast < n; fast++){

    if(condition){
        arr[slow] = arr[fast];
        slow++;
    }
}
```

---

# Template 3: Fast Slow

```java
ListNode slow = head;
ListNode fast = head;

while(fast != null && fast.next != null){

    slow = slow.next;
    fast = fast.next.next;
}
```

---

# Template 4: Sliding Window

```java
int left = 0;

for(int right = 0; right < n; right++){

    while(windowInvalid){
        left++;
    }
}
```

