# 8. Time Complexity Analysis

Why O(N)?

Because each pointer moves at most N times.

Example:

```java
while(left < right){
   left++;
   right--;
}
```

Total movements:

```text
N
```

not

```text
N²
```

Therefore:

```text
Time = O(N)

Space = O(1)
```

