# 11. Common Mistakes

---

## Mistake 1

Wrong Loop

Wrong:

```java
while(left <= right)
```

Correct:

```java
while(left < right)
```

---

## Mistake 2

Forgetting Sorted Condition

Two Sum using Two Pointers requires:

```text
Sorted Array
```

---

## Mistake 3

Infinite Loop

Wrong:

```java
while(left < right){
}
```

No pointer movement.

Always move pointers.

---

## Mistake 4

Pointer Out of Bounds

Always check:

```java
fast != null
&&
fast.next != null
```

